\begin_layout Subsection
Overview
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
In order to made our practices of the module Web Apps Deployment from the
 second course of WAD, our teacher propose us using the operative system
 Ubuntu 18.04.06 LTS.
 This operative system has several advantages that make it ideal for the
 objectives that we have:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
It is free.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
It has lot of documentation on the internet.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
It is a LTS (Long Term Support) version.
 That means that it is going to be supported until 2023.
 This is synonym of stability, a needed feature in a server.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
It has all the essential programs to set up a web server.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Due to all these arguments, we are going to make an installation of it on
 a virtual machine on the next sections.
\end_layout

